reviewText: I ordered an evening with the legends of gospel and received Chinese comic books. I am not pleased with my order. There is no way these should be mixed up  (dvd/books).
A great selection of Live performances of Gospel music. These groups will bring you joy any day of the week .

I love this CD. I having been playing it every day since I received it in the mail. This is traditional gospel at its best. You do not hear singing like this every day. You must add it to your gospel music collection.
I got this DVD for my mom it was her 80th birthday and she loved every bit of it hasn't stopped listening to it since excellent!!
this is the gospel music my parents grew up with and i love.  i played it for my family on Christmas day.  we never got to the Christmas music.
Great DVD of incredible performances with these legends of quartet gospel.  I truly enjoyed it.
This was one of my favorites I had to go back and get a second one for a family member
